    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a pristine 1994 Toyota Supra Turbo, a definitive example of JDM engineering. This A80 chassis houses the legendary 2JZ-GTE inline-six, featuring a sequential twin-turbocharger setup and cast-iron block for unparalleled thermal stability. Power is delivered through the robust V160 Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a Torsen limited-slip differential. The suspension remains factory-spec with its sophisticated aluminum double-wishbone architecture, ensuring precise kinematic control. This vehicle has undergone a rigorous mechanical inspection; the compression ratios across all six cylinders are within factory tolerances, and the turbo seals show zero oil bypass. The exterior retains its original VIN-matching panels with high-gloss depth, while the undercarriage is free of oxidation or fluid seepage. A true collector-grade specimen for the discerning purist.",
