      "description": "Presenting a truly investment-grade example that redefines the standard for pre-owned excellence. This vehicle remains in showroom-fresh state, boasting its original, mirror-finish paintwork protected by a professional ceramic coating. The interior is equally impeccable; the premium leather still retains its factory-new scent, and every electronic component operates with tactile precision. Under the hood, the engine bay is detailed to a concours level, backed by a comprehensive, documented service history from day one. With zero curb rash on the wheels and deep tread on the performance tires, this car offers a turn-key experience for the most discerning collector. It has been strictly garage-kept and climate-controlled, ensuring no UV damage or environmental wear. This is not just a car; it is a meticulously preserved piece of automotive history.",
