    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy, and honestly, she\u2019s in such incredible shape you\u2019d think she just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one\u2014not a scratch, no weird smells, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you\u2019re looking for that 'new car' feeling without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. I've taken care of every little detail so you don't have to. Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
