    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six with individual throttle bodies and a 7,900 RPM redline. This specimen has undergone a comprehensive mechanical baseline, including a Beisan Systems double-VANOS overhaul and a precise valve shim adjustment. The chassis integrity is guaranteed via proactive rear subframe reinforcement with structural plates. The drivetrain features a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory variable M differential lock, providing exceptional torque transfer. Suspension kinematics remain sharp with fresh OEM bushings and dampers. The exterior retains its factory-applied finish with no evidence of panel replacement or paint correction, while the interior displays zero bolster wear or pixel degradation in the cluster. This is a mechanically superlative example for the purist collector.",
